{"descriptions":[{"id":355,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp\u003eExamples: ཆུང་ཆུང་, ཐག་ཉེ་པོ་, ཆེན་པོ་, རིལ་རིལ་, རྙིང་པ་, དཀར་པོ་\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":false,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:35 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:35 UTC","authors":[{"id":"2","fullname":"David Germano"}]},{"id":356,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe positive form of adjectives is formed by adding \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔོ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམོ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམ་\u003c/span\u003e to the short form (xxlink above) of the adjective, or by doubling up the short form (in the case of adjectives like (\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆུང་ཆུང་\u003c/span\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eExamples of the long form of adjectives are: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྐྱིད་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;pleasant,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདཀར་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;white,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགསལ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;clear,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམང་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;many,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྟོང་པ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;empty,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབཙོག་པ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;dirty\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགཙང་མ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;clean,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགསར་པ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;new,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྙིང་པ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;old,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམངར་མོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;sweet,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགྲང་མོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;cold,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐུང་ཐུང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;short,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆུང་ཆུང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;small,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལེབ་ལེབ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;flat,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྒོར་སྒོར་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;round, circular,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརིལ་རིལ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;spherical, cylindrical,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐང་ཐང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;healthy,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཉུང་ཉུང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;few,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསོབ་སོབ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;soft,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལྷོད་ལྷོད་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;relaxed,\u0026rdquo; etc.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eCertain adjectives are formed by means of an expression comprising a substantive followed by an adjective such as \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཚ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;hot\u0026rdquo; (often pejorative), \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆེན་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;big,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབདེ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;well,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདོད་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;shape, appearance,\u0026rdquo; etc.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eExamples of these are: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསེམས་བཟང་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;kind,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལག་པ་དམ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;greedy,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཇུས་གཏོགས་ཚ་བོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;curious,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགཡོ་སྒྱུ་ཚ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;hypocritical,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཧམ་པ་ཚ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;arrogant, brutal,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཞེད་སྣང་ཚ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;scary, terrible,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐག་ཉེ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;close, near,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམངོན་གསལ་དོད་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;manifest, obvious,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལྟ་བཟོ་དོད་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;superb,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགཙང་སྦྲ་དོད་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;impeccable,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབློ་ཁོག་ཆེན་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;brave,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྟབས་བདེ་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;convenient.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:35 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:07:35 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}